We are a local, family-owned house cleaning service business, serving customers throughout Peterborough, Ontario and the Kawarthas.

We offer house cleaning, junk removal, construction clean-up, window repair, defogging and window installation services. Our team members are thoroughly trained and will treat your home and property with the utmost of care and respect.
